{"tid":560974,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術賈曉晨］屎眼啲毛 到底有咩用","createTime":"2018-02-14T14:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T11:48:21.000Z","uid":2333,"like":338,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"237ca39c36c779b2190f4339ca43067c3b4e2509","tid":560974,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"陰毛就話用來緩衝扑嘢既撞擊<br />\n<br />\n咁屎眼啲毛係咪都係相同作用<br />\n神一早預設左我地會肛交？<br />\n<br />\n定還是預示左同性戀也是正常<br />\n可惜碌鳩太長？"},{"pid":"a5cbc7a4e531bd3acc5e148ac505755b764730ba","tid":560974,"uid":4574,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"千"},{"pid":"3027927b5f26606013b0a2682e0a495a058e14bc","tid":560974,"uid":27421,"like":387,"dislike":3,"score":384,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"你都係想人地貼潮文姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc45cd1c217541d16060c9300337629dfce3d304","tid":560974,"uid":48112,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"好耐冇聽呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea718841f17ccfa828eac0428e742c30d85d502f","tid":560974,"uid":25635,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a5cbc7a4e531bd3acc5e148ac505755b764730ba","tid":560974,"uid":4574,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"千"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"萬"},{"pid":"0474888b82c8b5956a43b9bd1db7bf92a49ce8a0","tid":560974,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6dc179fa644fa04b1a7517266b23368bdc7e107d","tid":560974,"uid":35730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea718841f17ccfa828eac0428e7